{"tid":1133012,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)末日先鋒：戰甲飛車","createTime":"2019-04-30T17:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T18:55:27.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b40d6d0cc7c772393a927820179b97e947e63428","tid":1133012,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T17:21:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=f4505a2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=626f17b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=0f540c2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a>&lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fb/Mad_Max_Fury_Road_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffb%2FMad_Max_Fury_Road_poster.jpg&h=81d7d072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在不遠的未來，人類文明因為核爆崩落後成為了荒漠世界，土壤酸化、沒有法治和憐憫，水和石油是珍貴的資源。前澳大利亞公路巡警麥斯一開始被軍閥領導的不死老喬手下的「戰爭男孩」捕獲，車子「XB攔截者」也被奪走並被帶到了不死老喬統治的「西方堡壘」；西方堡壘是一個富有綠意和水資源的峽谷形軍闊，但貧民只能待在堡壘下方讓老喬釋放的地下水來維生。麥斯被剪了頭髮並被判定為「強效型供血者」，作為半死不活的戰爭男孩奈克斯的「血袋」。同時，不死老喬在堡壘上放下了水給下面的貧民們，並派往指揮官芙莉歐莎駕駛著「武裝運輸車」到煉油廠採集汽油回來。芙莉歐莎等人出發後不久，老喬發現她偏離了路線和自己的五位妻妾「種母」也不見了；老喬開出「億馬千軍號」便帶領著整個戰爭男孩軍隊與「電音花車」負責指揮去將芙莉歐莎追回，並也找來了煤氣鎮與子彈農場的同夥來幫忙<br />\n<br />\n2 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=11811727\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=a7b86d9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb80c059cb3faca945966c685a36028288f46010","tid":1133012,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a6885da69756a10bd3d8f330e87681dca2eecc","tid":1133012,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}